<A HREF="links.phtml"><B>Links:</B></A><BR>
<FONT SIZE="2" FACE="ARIEL">
Reworked the links pages a bit, adding a new section for specialized links to sites that showcase specific EQ information. I also added links to the two popular sites <A HREF="http://www.eqmaps.com" TARGET="_new">EQ Maps</A> and <A HREF="http://www.eqatlas.com" TARGET="_new">EQ Atlas</A>.</FONT><BR><BR>

<A HREF="tales.phtml"><B>Norrathian Tales:</B></A><BR>
<FONT SIZE="2" FACE="ARIEL">
Just added another excellant story by our talented writer <A HREF="mem_detail.php3?search=585"></A>Nalfein</A> entitled "Diary of a Dark Elf - <A HREF="/stories/diary1.phtml">Part 1</A> ".</FONT><BR><BR> 

<A HREF="main.phtml#1.0 Poll"><B>Polls:</B></A><BR>
<FONT SIZE="2" FACE="ARIEL">
Here are the results from last weeks' poll question <I></I>"Do you have, or ever had, at least one character that is/was level 30 or above?"</I><BR><BR>

<B>1. Yes:</B> 50.21% (244 votes)<BR>
<B>2. No:</B> 49.79% (242 votes)<BR>
<B>-------------------</B><BR>
<B>Total Votes:</B> 486</FONT><BR><BR>

<FONT SIZE="2" FACE="ARIEL">
As you can see, after 486 votes the results were almost dead even between players who have gotten a character above level 30 and those who haven't yet. I believe this illustrates how much the player base has matured and why Verant seems to be concentrating on adding higher level zones lately.<BR><BR>

This weeks new poll question is <I>"If you have the expansion pack, about how often do you play in the new Kunark zones?"</I></FONT><BR><BR>

<A HREF="screenshots.phtml"><B>Daily Kunark Image:</B></A><BR>
<FONT SIZE="2" FACE="ARIEL">
We still need more screenshots for our "Kunark Daily Image" on our main page, so if you see a nice sunset, dungeon, beast or castle.... make sure you take a nice picture and <A HREF="mailto:madwand@home.com">mail</A> it to us !
</FONT><BR><BR>

<B><I>MadWand</I></B><BR><BR></FONT></TD></TR></TABLE>	
